From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: sarun <noreply@sarun>
Date: Sun, 19 Jul 2026 11:12:13 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] find: expose shared file-type syntax catalog

Define the -type and -xtype predicates, their finite native value domain, list separator, and uniqueness rule in immutable find-owned metadata. Make top-level parsing and execution validation consume that same catalog so grammar importers cannot drift from runtime acceptance.

---
